videos.headline: Robinson runs into end zone for Bama TD
videos.description: Alabama strikes first as Brian Robinson Jr. rushes in for an 8-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Robinson runs into end zone for Bama TD) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Long catch sets up 8-yard TD as Tennessee squares things up
videos.description: Hendon Hooker completes a 39-yard pass to set up an 8-yard Velus Jones touchdown catch for the Volunteers.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Long catch sets up 8-yard TD as Tennessee squares things up) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: JaVonta Payton makes a man miss for the 57-yard TD
videos.description: JaVonta Payton hauls in a pass from Hendon Hooker and puts the Volunteers in control.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (JaVonta Payton makes a man miss for the 57-yard TD) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young improvises with 5-yard TD scramble
videos.description: Bryce Young makes the play with his feet as he rushes in for a 5-yard Alabama touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young improvises with 5-yard TD scramble) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young threads it through tight window for Bama TD
videos.description: Bryce Young finds John Metchie III through a narrow opening for a 6-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Young improvises with 5-yard TD scramble) 2021/10/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Young pump fakes his way to his 2nd rushing TD
videos.description: Bryce Young scrambles into the end zone to extend Alabama's lead to 14.

videos.headline: Tillman torches Bama DB for 70-yard TD catch
videos.description: Cedric Tillman runs past the Alabama secondary and hauls in a 70-yard TD catch.

videos.headline: Alabama capitalizes off INT with rushing TD

videos.headline: Alabama puts the game to bed with 18-yard Metchie TD
videos.description: John Metchie III runs into the end zone for the 18-yard touchdown catch as Alabama leads 52-17.

videos.headline: Bama's Saban is 'really happy' to beat Tennessee
videos.description: Despite having mental lapses in a tough game, No. 4 Alabama's Nick Saban is elated to walk away with a win against Tennessee.

videos.headline: No. 4 Bama's stout ground game fends off tenacious Vols
videos.description: Alabama's Brian Robinson Jr. and Bryce Young total five rushing TDs to help overcome a slow first half, defeating relentless Tennessee, 52-24.
